<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> | MiSitio Express</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row align-items-center g-5">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <span class="badge bg-info text-dark mb-3">Sobre Nosotros</span>
                <h2 class="display-6 fw-bold mb-4">Construimos el futuro <span class="text-info">digital</span></h2>
                <p class="lead text-muted">Somos un equipo enfocado en crear soluciones web limpias, escalables y fáciles de mantener.</p>
                <p class="text-muted">Este proyecto demuestra la integración de <strong>Express.js</strong> como servidor, <strong>EJS</strong> como motor de plantillas y <strong>Bootstrap 5</strong> para la interfaz visual.</p>
                <div class="d-flex gap-2 mt-4 flex-wrap">
                    <span class="badge bg-light text-dark border">Node.js</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-light text-dark border">Express</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-light text-dark border">EJS</span>
                    <span class="badge bg-light text-dark border">Bootstrap 5</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-lg p-4">
                    <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center py-3"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-3"></i> Rutas organizadas y escalables</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center py-3"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-3"></i> Partials reutilizables (Header/Footer)</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center py-3"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-3"></i> Diseño 100% responsivo</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center py-3"><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success me-3"></i> Manejo de errores y 404 personalizado</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>